title: 11/05/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Brady Quinn about whether he thinks Cincy will be left out of the College Football Playoffs. Steelers QB Ben Roethlisberger tells us about trolling Coach Tomlin with USC gear. And Mike Florio provides more insight into the Aaron Rodgers situation.
